"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Gm frens.\\n\\nWe have successfully launched the first phase of OnlyFrens eehhh **[frens.page](https://frens.page)**.\\n\\n**As of today, pages have the following features:**\\n\\n* Choose one of your .eth ENS domains & set your username\\n* Choose one of your NFTs as profile pic\\n* Add a small biography and links to your page (max 4 rows)\\n* Add a Twitter profile\\n* Send donations to your frens\\n\\nAs reference, this is how our page now looks like: [frens.page/frenspage.eth](https://frens.page/frenspage.eth)\\n\\n![frens.page/frenspage.eth](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_JEhzWzCKdKEE5es27X5i.png?height=572&width=1679&&&&&&&&&&&&size=large)\\n\\n## Next is Phase 2 - the Content Phase.\\n\\nThe next big phase on the roadmap will be the “**content phase**”.\\nSoon, frens will be able to add content pieces to their pages (Images and Texts, later Videos).\\n\\nWe have planned a different kind of interface from what you may know from other social networks.\\n\\nThis is how the interface will look like:\\n\\n![An example frens.page with content](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/AKEXgc4ysa7SDqZlzvMh5.png?height=763&width=1351&&&&&&&&&&&&size=large)\\n\\nFrens will add their content pieces on a canvas and thus “clip” them to their pages.\\n\\nFrens will need to replace content over time.\\n\\n![Add content to your pages.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/cVXr35ttzdz3yVx0p-IuU.jpg?height=1080&width=1920&&&&size=large)\\n\\nThe available space will be limited, like on a whiteboard.\\n\\nFrens must use it wisely.\\n\\nVisitors will need to bookmark the good pages of their frens.\\n\\nHere’s another simple example:\\n\\n![Another example frens.page](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/hbRBiK9pKTfVvo5XSR84F.jpg?height=1080&width=1920&&&size=large)\\n\\n### No scrollable feeds\\n\\nWe don’t want to replicate endless feeds, infinite scrolling, or classic ads - legacy mechanics that are responsible for quite some trouble on existing social networks.\\n\\nWeb3 social networks need to be better than this.\\n\\nAs they should not rely on ads, there should be fewer incentives for any platform to optimize for maximum user attention spans.\\n\\nFrens.page does not want to bombard you with posts by people or bots that you don’t know. We choose an approach that reduces the external influence of corporate and mass media as much as possible.\\n\\nThe baseline is:\\n\\nFrens.page should be fun.\\nFrens choose what they want to see.\\nNo funny business by corporate trolls.\\n\\n***It will be like back in the good old days.***\\n\\nAlso, we have a cool idea for phase 3, but we can’t tease it yet.\\n\\nThe future of frens will be glorious.\\n\\n## Before we build Phase 2: Phase “1.5.”\\n\\nThere are a few things we need to prepare in order to successfully build phase 2.\\n\\n1. We will integrate more native ENS features so that you can choose to automagically import your pfp, twitter, and description directly from ENS. Thx to all the people who suggested this.\\n2. We need to implement a method to check whether you still own your pfp and .eth NFTs. Therefore an automated check will be built soon.\\n3. We’re currently relying on the OpenSea API to display NFTs and their metadata. We may need to implement a fallback API for cases when OpenSea is down.\\n4. We may consider adding an “About” page to provide a bit more information on what frens.page is all about.\\n\\nRemember, frens.page is an open-source project. If you want to contribute, feel free to do so here:\\n\\n[https://github.com/frenspage/frenspage](https://github.com/frenspage/frenspage)\\n\\nAlso, consider joining our Discord and ask for the “Dev” role if you want to help buidling.\\n\\n[https://discord.gg/QAATuupP](https://discord.gg/QAATuupP)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641218246,\"title\":\"Frens.page - Announcing Phase 2\"},\"digest\":\"LwYWzdjqSMYNi76IREl0zyj2tqj5VK0nqDyEGGImVZM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x390147288E480B1457E49CA174bB9f2290B88dbB\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"H0zLIoy_ef5ytjVBNTggXNpxgWCFasTDAMvBWZLzCTU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"v6Hoydpjg-uD7hoy-V3E796QOEImrz3wuCB_cP9TK7I\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"hh0jfdiww30QYCJKwO9fCMJMKMcN2v4bc2acIK2cdwOG1DcL63iYGZddx6foIZLeojUOjuAmTBTIvHoEyKyzRg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xaff68898b89a11e07fba69bfb186d37f1cab73c4a4cb713a71cba02a813c6138263ec978051b7aa0ff4a30e18b344a10dd51668d30f56a96cc9120ec5043a26b1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"H0zLIoy_ef5ytjVBNTggXNpxgWCFasTDAMvBWZLzCTU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"v6Hoydpjg-uD7hoy-V3E796QOEImrz3wuCB_cP9TK7I\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"DKmcPvdzgSQ2sXsdNE8ywu6aQr3wextS5KKQwAZ9XqM\"}"